==製作==
===發展===
2018年7月，執行製作{{link-en|史考特·M·金普|Scott M. Gimple}}在[[聖地亞哥國際漫畫展|聖地亞哥國際漫畫展]]時宣佈，《[[陰屍路|陰屍路]]》的第二部衍生劇正在製作中<ref name="Gimple2018">{{cite web |url=http://comicbook.com/thewalkingdead/2018/07/21/the-walking-dead-spinoff-comic-con-scott-gimple |title='The Walking Dead' Executive Producer Planning Another Spinoff |website=Comicbook.com |first=Cameron |last=Bonomolo |date=2018-07-21 |accessdate=2019-10-13 |archive-date=2019-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411004113/https://comicbook.com/thewalkingdead/2018/07/21/the-walking-dead-spinoff-comic-con-scott-gimple/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年4月，[[AMC_(电视频道)|AMC電視台]]預定衍生劇首季的10集，劇名暫定為《紀念碑》（{{lang|en|''Monument''}}）<ref name="ThirdSpinoff">{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/04/the-walking-dead-spinoff-details-revealed-by-amc-ahead-of-2020-premiere-1202590997/ |title='Walking Dead' Spinoff Greenlighted By AMC For 2020 Premiere, Details Revealed |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |first=Dade |last=Hayes |date=2019-04-08 |accessdate=2019-10-13 |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822100853/https://deadline.com/2019/04/the-walking-dead-spinoff-details-revealed-by-amc-ahead-of-2020-premiere-1202590997/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Monument">{{cite web |url=https://comicbook.com/thewalkingdead/2019/07/26/walking-dead-spinoff-title-plane-crash-monument-virginia/ |title=Walking Dead Spinoff's Working Title, Major Pilot Episode Details Revealed |website=Comicbook.com |first=Brandon |last=Davis |date=2019-07-26 |accessdate=2019-10-13 |archive-date=2019-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191016194217/https://comicbook.com/thewalkingdead/2019/07/26/walking-dead-spinoff-title-plane-crash-monument-virginia/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年11月24日，金普正式公佈劇名為《-{zh-tw:陰屍路：劫後餘生; zh-hk:陰屍路：化外世界; zh-cn:行尸走肉：外面的世界}-》<ref name="Title">{{cite web |last=Ausiello |first=Michael |title=Third Walking Dead Series Gets Title |url=https://tvline.com/2019/11/24/the-walking-dead-world-beyond-third-series-title-amc/ |website=[[TVLine|TVLine]] |date=2019-11-24 |accessdate=2019-11-25 |archive-date=2019-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191126024236/https://tvline.com/2019/11/24/the-walking-dead-world-beyond-third-series-title-amc/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年1月，AMC公佈劇集將會播出兩季，每季各有10集，包括在2020年4月12日首播<ref name="TwoSeasons">{{cite web |last=O'Dell |first=Johnny |title=The Walking Dead: World Beyond Will Only Last Two Seasons |url=https://www.skybound.com/shows/the-walking-dead-world-beyond/the-walking-dead-world-beyond-will-only-last-two-seasons |website=[[Skybound_Entertainment|Skybound Entertainment]] |date=2020-01-16 |accessdate=2020-01-16 |archive-date=2020-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125222633/https://www.skybound.com/shows/the-walking-dead-world-beyond/the-walking-dead-world-beyond-will-only-last-two-seasons |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="PremiereDate">{{cite web |url=https://tvline.com/2020/01/16/the-walking-dead-world-beyond-premiere-date-amc-photos/ |title=The Walking Dead: World Beyond Premiere Date Is Set at AMC — Plus, Feast Your Eyes On the Latest Photos |website=[[TVLine|TVLine]] |first=Charlie |last=Mason |date=2020-01-16 |accessdate=2020-01-16 |archive-date=2020-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200225080944/https://tvline.com/2020/01/16/the-walking-dead-world-beyond-premiere-date-amc-photos/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年3月，劇集受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影響而延期播出，改在2020年10月4日時首播<ref>{{cite web |url=https://tvline.com/2020/03/20/the-walking-dead-world-beyond-delayed-postponed-spinoff-premiere-date/ |title=Walking Dead Spinoff World Beyond Postponed, New Premiere Date TBD |first=Dave |last=Nemetz |website=[[TVLine|TVLine]] |date=2020-03-20 |accessdate=2020-03-20 |archive-date=2020-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320231515/https://tvline.com/2020/03/20/the-walking-dead-world-beyond-delayed-postponed-spinoff-premiere-date/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年7月，AMC宣佈本劇作為最終季的第二季定於2021年10月3日首播。<ref name="S2Premiere">{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2021/07/walking-dead-world-beyond-season-2-premiere-date-amc-1234799151/ |title='The Walking Dead: World Beyond' Reveals Final-Season Premiere Date And First Look – Comic-Con |website=Deadline Hollywood |first=Dominic |last=Patten |date=2021-07-23 |accessdate=2021-07-23 |archive-date=2022-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220215093753/https://deadline.com/2021/07/walking-dead-world-beyond-season-2-premiere-date-amc-1234799151/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===選角===
2019年7月，艾莉莎·曼蘇（{{lang|en|Alexa Mansour}}），{{link-en|尼可拉斯·坎圖|Nicolas Cantu}}與哈爾·坎普斯頓（{{lang|en|Hal Cumpston}}）加盟劇集作為領銜主演<ref name="July2019Casting">{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/third-walking-dead-series-cast-1203262504/ |title=New 'Walking Dead' Series Casts Three Lead Roles (EXCLUSIVE) |website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |first=Joe |last=Otterson |date=2019-07-10 |accessdate=2019-10-13 |archive-date=2020-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200302183033/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/third-walking-dead-series-cast-1203262504/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同一月，艾莉婭·羅耶爾（{{lang|en|Aliyah Royale}}）和[[安妮特·莫翰德魯|安妮特·莫翰德魯]]加盟劇集<ref name="RoyaleMahendru">{{cite web |url=https://tvline.com/2019/07/19/walking-dead-third-series-annet-mahendru-cast/ |title=Third Walking Dead Series Adds Americans' Annet Mahendru to Cast |website=[[TVLine|TVLine]] |date=2019-07-19 |first=Matt Webb |last=Mitovich |accessdate=2019-10-13 |archive-date=2019-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806115612/https://tvline.com/2019/07/19/walking-dead-third-series-annet-mahendru-cast/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。緊接著加盟劇集的有[[尼可·托托雷拉|尼可·托托雷拉]]<ref name="Tortorella">{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/the-walking-dead-third-series-nico-tortorella-star-cast-new-spinoff-amc-1202661133/ |title='The Walking Dead' Third Series: Nico Tortorella To Star In New Spinoff On AMC |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |date=2019-08-05 |accessdate=2019-10-13 |archive-date=2020-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200214155211/https://deadline.com/2019/08/the-walking-dead-third-series-nico-tortorella-star-cast-new-spinoff-amc-1202661133/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及著名演員[[茱莉亞·歐蒙|茱莉亞·歐蒙]]。歐蒙將在劇中飾演伊莉莎白·庫布爾克（{{lang|en|Lt. Col. Elizabeth Kublek}}），角色身為「一名充滿魅力的領袖，領導著一股強大且複雜的勢力。」<ref name="Ormond">{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/walking-dead-world-beyond-julia-ormond-casting-1203415154/ |title='The Walking Dead: World Beyond' Casts Julia Ormond |first=Danielle |last=Turchiano |date=2019-11-24 |accessdate=2019-11-24 |website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |archive-date=2019-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191222062511/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/walking-dead-world-beyond-julia-ormond-casting-1203415154/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2019年8月，喬·霍特（{{lang|en|Joe Holt}}）加盟劇集作為常設演員<ref name="Holt">{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/the-walking-dead-third-series-joe-holt-recur-new-spinoff-amc-1202667465/ |title='The Walking Dead' Third Series: Joe Holt To Recur In New Spinoff On AMC |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |first=Denise |last=Petski |date=2019-08-14 |accessdate=2019-10-16 |archive-date=2019-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211205614/https://deadline.com/2019/08/the-walking-dead-third-series-joe-holt-recur-new-spinoff-amc-1202667465/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在11月，另外四名演員加盟劇集作為常設，{{link-en|娜塔莉·高德|Natalie Gold}}、阿爾·卡德隆（{{lang|en|Al Calderon}}）、{{link-en|史考特·阿西特|Scott Adsit}}和泰德·蘇德蘭（{{lang|en|Ted Sutherland}}），分別飾演角色萊拉（{{lang|en|Lyla}}）、巴薩（{{lang|en|Barca}}）、東尼（{{lang|en|Tony}}）和波西（{{lang|en|Percy}}）<ref name="Ormond" />。

===拍攝===
劇集拍攝工作於2019年7月在美國[[維吉尼亞州|維吉尼亞州]][[里士满_(弗吉尼亚州)|里士滿]]開始，預計在2019年11月末結束<ref name="FirstTeaser2019">{{cite web |url=https://comicbook.com/thewalkingdead/2019/07/30/the-walking-dead-first-trailer-for-third-series-released/ |title=The Walking Dead: First Trailer For Third Series Released |website=Comicbook.com |first=Russ |last=Burlingame |date=2019-07-29 |accessdate=2019-10-13 |archive-date=2019-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925204826/https://comicbook.com/thewalkingdead/2019/07/30/the-walking-dead-first-trailer-for-third-series-released/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而導演[[喬丹·沃格特-羅伯茲|喬丹·沃格特-羅伯茲]]原計劃將會執導首播集<ref name="ProductionStarts">{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/walking-dead-full-cast-set-third-show-amc-1225727 |title='The Walking Dead': Full Cast Set for Third Show on AMC |first=Lesley |last=Goldberg |date=2019-07-19 |accessdate=2019-07-21 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |archive-date=2019-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721212931/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/walking-dead-full-cast-set-third-show-amc-1225727 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，然而由於編劇決定將整部劇集採用另一風格，首播集導演則更換成執導過《[[驚嚇陰屍路|驚嚇陰屍路]]》的梅格納斯·馬滕斯<ref name="Magnus Martens">{{cite web |url=https://www.tvguide.com/news/the-walking-dead-world-beyond-matthew-negrete-interview/ |title=The Walking Dead: World Beyond Boss Says You Don't Have to Be Caught Up on TWD to Watch the Spin-Off |website=TV Guide |first=Liam |last=Matthews |date=2020-10-01 |accessdate=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008032248/https://www.tvguide.com/news/the-walking-dead-world-beyond-matthew-negrete-interview/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同時保留沃格特-羅伯茲提供的故事點子。劇集除了會在著名美劇《[[迷失|迷失]]》拍攝“墜機場景”的同一地點取景以外，在2019年8月的前兩星期還會在維吉尼亞州[[霍普維爾_(維吉尼亞州)|霍普維爾]]拍攝<ref name="Monument"/>。

